link: A. Karttunen, Alternative Catalan Orderings (with the complete Scheme source)
Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
program: (Scheme functions showing the essential idea. For the complete source, follow the "Alternative Catalan Orderings" link:)

(define (Nvector->primefactorization! el) (let loop ((el (reverse! el)) (i 1) (z 1)) (cond ((null? el) z) ((null? (cdr el)) (* (expt (A008578 i) (car el)) z)) (else (loop (cdr el) (1+ i) (* (expt (A008578 i) (-1+ (car el))) z))))))
